    <title>萌娘百科中黑幕的实现</title>
    <url>/billypung.github.io/2020/03/29/%E8%90%8C%E5%A8%98%E7%99%BE%E7%A7%91%E4%B8%AD%E9%BB%91%E5%B9%95%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="摘要"><a href="#摘要" class="headerlink" title="摘要"></a>摘要</h1><p>想实现类似于萌娘百科上词条中常会出现的黑幕，自己研究一番后放弃，最后参考一位大佬的博客得以实现。</p>
<a id="more"></a>

<h1 id="正文"><a href="#正文" class="headerlink" title="正文"></a>正文</h1><h2 id="声明"><a href="#声明" class="headerlink" title="声明"></a>声明</h2><p>本功能及代码最终来源于<a href="https://moegirl.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">萌娘百科</a></p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">本文引自萌娘百科(https://zh.moegirl.org)，文字内容默认使用《知识共享 署名-非商业性使用-相同方式共享 3.0》协议。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>以及参考自<em>此夜曲中闻折柳</em>的<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/send-off-a-friend/p/12355387.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">博客文章</a></p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">https://www.cnblogs.com/send-off-a-friend/p/12355387.html</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>注：若有引用声明错误或格式错误，请提醒我，我将立马更改。谢谢！</p>
<h2 id="代码内容"><a href="#代码内容" class="headerlink" title="代码内容"></a>代码内容</h2><p>在“定制css代码”文件中加入以下内容</p>
<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.heimu</span>, <span class="selector-class">.heimu</span> <span class="selector-tag">a</span>, <span class="selector-tag">a</span> <span class="selector-class">.heimu</span>, <span class="selector-class">.heimu</span> <span class="selector-tag">a</span><span class="selector-class">.new</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">background-color</span>: <span class="number">#252525</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">color</span>: <span class="number">#252525</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">text-shadow</span>: none;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.heimu</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:hover</span>, <span class="selector-class">.heimu</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:active</span>,</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.heimu</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:hover</span> <span class="selector-class">.heimu</span>, <span class="selector-class">.heimu</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:active</span> <span class="selector-class">.heimu</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">color</span>: white <span class="meta">!important</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.heimu</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:hover</span> <span class="selector-tag">a</span>, <span class="selector-tag">a</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:hover</span> <span class="selector-class">.heimu</span>,</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.heimu</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:active</span> <span class="selector-tag">a</span>, <span class="selector-tag">a</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:active</span> <span class="selector-class">.heimu</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">color</span>: lightblue <span class="meta">!important</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.heimu</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:hover</span> <span class="selector-class">.new</span>, <span class="selector-class">.heimu</span> <span class="selector-class">.new</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:hover</span>, <span class="selector-class">.new</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:hover</span> <span class="selector-class">.heimu</span>,</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.heimu</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:active</span> <span class="selector-class">.new</span>, <span class="selector-class">.heimu</span> <span class="selector-class">.new</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:active</span>, <span class="selector-class">.new</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:active</span> <span class="selector-class">.heimu</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">color</span>: <span class="number">#BA0000</span> <span class="meta">!important</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*阅读更多：https://zh.moegirl.org/MediaWiki:Mobile.css 本文引自萌娘百科(https://zh.moegirl.org)，文字内容默认使用《知识共享 署名-非商业性使用-相同方式共享 3.0》协议。*/</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>根据我浅薄的html语法知识，这里是增加了一个<i><span title="class">类</span></i>，之后在文章中使用span标签即可。</p>
<h2 id="使用代码"><a href="#使用代码" class="headerlink" title="使用代码"></a>使用代码</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"heimu"</span> <span class="attr">title</span>=<span class="string">"Mon Panache!"</span>&gt;</span>Cynaro最后一句话是？<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><span class="heimu" title="Mon Panache!">Cynaro最后一句话是？</span></p>
<p>但似乎黑幕的提示字在电脑上不是那么快可以反应出来，在手机上也无法显示title内容，待研究。</p>
<h2 id="啥是黑幕？"><a href="#啥是黑幕？" class="headerlink" title="啥是黑幕？"></a>啥是黑幕？</h2><p>这个问题懒得解释，自己看：</p>
<p><span class="heimu" title="你知道的太多了">这就是所谓黑幕</span></p>
<h1 id="顺带的话"><a href="#顺带的话" class="headerlink" title="顺带的话"></a>顺带的话</h1><p>似乎使用以下批注方式</p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">被批注内容[^1]</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">^1</span>]: <span class="link">解释内容</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这样的形式不是太方便，甚至还出现了不能正常识别为批注的情况。</p>
<p>所以，有时候我也会采用</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">*<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">title</span>=<span class="string">"解释内容"</span>&gt;</span>被解释内容<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span>*<span class="comment">&lt;!-- 已废！--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- *符号为Markdown的斜体符号 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- 好吧，不这样用了，Markdown和html混用在手机上似乎渲染不出来，还是使用单纯的html吧--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span> <span class="attr">title</span>=<span class="string">"解释内容"</span>&gt;</span>被解释内容<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这样的形式来批注内容。</p>
<p>但不论怎么批注，在手机上显示始终有问题，待解决。</p>
<p>如果你有更好的方法，请务必在下方给我这个小白留言，或私信我，谢谢！</p>
]]></content>
